Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:20.09,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I put together dried up words...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:28.83,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but all I want to do is convey\N my simple feelings to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:34.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The faint wind that blew from that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:38.40,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I threw it away in yesterday's ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:44.55,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So I can live today with you with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:52.19,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But still, this incident will\N continue to trouble you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:57.08,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's why it must be a goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:01:04.12,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now we just try to understand\N each other until nothing remains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:11.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And eventually, we will realize\N that it was everything to us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:18.01,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Sadness will run down our cheeks,\N creating a river of tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:28.97,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,1700)}Trembling thoughts will become a strong\N whirl and melt together into one
Comment: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:30.04,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sand Coffin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Please back me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I got sand in my mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be able to do\Nanything in your current state...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy attacks with bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Like earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,he does things like shoot bones\Nand extrude bones from inside his body...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He controls bones freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara of the Desert...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You use sand,\Nas the name implies, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:12.17,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(478,597)}Showdown of the Strongest!\NGaara vs. Kimimaro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Showdown of the Strongest!\NGaara vs. Kimimaro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough defense using sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He... isn't a close-range combat type...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting close would be difficult, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Digital Shrapnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no waste in his movements...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough,\Nhe's a considerable Taijutsu user.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack and defense are one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He attacks and defends\Nwith sand, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the amount of sand\Nhe can control is probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...about the amount of sand\Ninside the gourd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara of the Desert...\NA dopey nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do anything\Nif you don't have sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to the trouble of walking around\Ncarrying heavy sand
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is the very proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sand Shower...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How trite...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I have sand,\NI can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who's dopey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy for me to do things\Nlike create sand with dirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,With his own sand he grinds things\Nlike rocks and minerals in dirt
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and makes it into sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was sending his own sand\Nbeneath the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and adding new sand, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara of the Desert...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,His nickname isn't just for display.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sand Burial!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm reminded of that man\Nwhen I look at that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uchiha Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He had the same eyes\Nas that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The same eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:06:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting to verify the value\Nof one's own existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Such eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here, aren't you?!\NAt least answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't hate the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The darkness is where\NI was brought up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I... in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there really God...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is, why confine me\Nin a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter who I am...\NGet out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimimaro, the time has come to use you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For our sake,\Nfor the Kaguya Clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... To fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the only thing I can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite some pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've been flattened\Njust like that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,had I not made a membrane\Nof bone just below the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bones... That guy's a monster, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a troublesome body, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I underestimated you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I won't be caught by\Nyour sand anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sand Tsunami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... It's beyond\Nthe scope of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,escaping from the sand\Nor not getting caught...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To think it would change\Nthe terrain itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant Sand Burial!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's so strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gotten even stronger\Nthan when he fought me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But... this time for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a persistent guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still... alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... There's still significance\Nfor me to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,From now, we're going\Nto launch a night attack
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,on the Hidden Mist Village...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As they are disconcerted\Nfrom that incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,now is the perfect time for us\Nto make them realize our ferocity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Make them realize the ferocity\Nof the Kaguya Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah!\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Kimimaro?\NGet going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to think\Ndeeply about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go down to the Hidden Mist Village
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and kill every last person\Nyou encounter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just act on your instincts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you of the Hidden Mist Village?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see... Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Haku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... no. It's nothing, Zabuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to be stopping.\NLet's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He had the same eyes as I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I met Zabuza...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a hasty one, aren't you?\NI'm not from this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing you are after is right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to have begun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kaguya Clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools who can only find\Ntheir own path of life by fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It was long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,when a simple-minded group that\Njust enjoyed slaughtering was acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,With a governed organization\Nas an opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.35,0:15:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,they just become fools\Nrushing towards death
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,if they fight only with power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we the only survivors...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems we're surrounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The defense was tighter\Nthan we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's come to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,take along with you\Nevery person you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:16:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have them entertain us\Nas much as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I fight for...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Without knowing anything,\NI just kept on fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come to use you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm needed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the only thing\Nthat got my body moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was also able to figure out that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't live if I didn't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dawn broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And I learned that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself was the only one\Nto survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, I'm all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:17:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,By myself, I just wandered\Naimlessly from place to place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The flower, from back then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you blooming\Nin a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're ignoring me, too, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you'd be seen\Nby someone in a place like this, yet you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe... there's no significance to living.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But you might be able to\Ndiscover something interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,by continuing to live... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how you discovered that flower...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how I discovered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then...\NLord Orochimaru said that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,People are born with\Nsome kind of significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I think...\Nsome kind of important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The mission for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is to protect Lord Orochimaru\Nand his ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's... that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back, Sasuke!\NEveryone's worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...\NIt's so dark I can't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got better eyes than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke is in the darkness now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Neji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be unable to catch up\Nwith Sasuke
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,if you stop in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Neji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... You're right!\NThis isn't the time to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:20:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait! I'll take Sasuke\Nback home no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sand Coffin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:20:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That form...?!
Comment: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:07.11,ED8,,0,0,0,,ED Start
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:15.41,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:18.50,ED8,,0,0,0,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:21.04,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:23.84,ED8,,0,0,0,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:29.48,ED8,,0,0,0,,Would you think it was\Na bother if I approached you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:34.89,ED8,,0,0,0,,Despite my doubts,\NI worked up my courage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:40.82,ED8,,0,0,0,,My clumsy attempts with words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:46.49,ED8,,0,0,0,,You listened without turning away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:52.61,ED8,,0,0,0,,No wonder I get carried away by you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.01,0:21:59.68,ED8,,0,0,0,,But you don't feel anything for me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:02.88,ED8,,0,0,0,,I feel so sad
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:03.85,ED8,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.85,0:22:06.32,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.32,0:22:09.36,ED8,,0,0,0,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:12.09,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.09,0:22:15.16,ED8,,0,0,0,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:17.67,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.67,0:22:20.87,ED8,,0,0,0,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.87,0:22:23.41,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.41,0:22:26.38,ED8,,0,0,0,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:31.01,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I spoke to you
